description: The future of a European democracy was being determined in Alaska last night without the presence of either that democracy or its European allies.
title: ANDREW NEIL: The world is being remade. And as the Alaska talks show all too clearly, Britain and Europe are now condemned to the status of mere observers

description: Not so long ago, dishevelled pictures like these would have been career suicide for Phillip Schofield. But today they represent something else entirely: his freedom.
title: Phillip Schofield is living his 'best gay life' as he enjoys late nights out with much younger man: Friends tell KATIE HIND how the ex presenter is 'making up for lost time' with new party circle... and reveal fresh Holly Willoughby snub

description: She has been busy promoting her new show, Channel 4's The Inheritance, whilst simultaneously pushing her capsule collection for her beachwear range.
title: Elizabeth Hurley reveals boyfriend Billy Ray Cyrus is teaching her how to play the guitar - as country singer pens 'sexy songs' inspired by her

description: The former This Morning presenter, 63, has long been open about her struggles with her weight, which have seen her fluctuate between a size 10 and 22.
title: Vanessa Feltz, 63, jokes 'looking gaunt is fantastic' as she joins Lizzie Cundy, 57, to discuss weight loss jabs after news Mounjaro cost is set to double
